<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">

<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title><%= seo ? seo.title : 'Agrim Classes' %></title>
<meta name="description" content="<%= seo ? seo.desc : 'Best Coaching Institute in Deoli' %>">
<meta name="keywords" content="<%= seo ? seo.keywords : 'education, coaching' %>">
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="style.css?v=1.1">
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/font-awesome/6.0.0/css/all.min.css">
    <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Poppins:wght@400;600;700&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
</head>

<body>

    <script src="header.js"></script>
    <my-header></my-header>

    <section class="breadcrumb-area">

        <div class="shape-globe">
            <svg width="60" height="60" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="#FFA500" stroke-width="1.5"
                stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round">
                <circle cx="12" cy="12" r="10"></circle>
                <path d="M2 12h20"></path>
                <path d="M12 2a15.3 15.3 0 0 1 4 10 15.3 15.3 0 0 1-4 10 15.3 15.3 0 0 1-4-10 15.3 15.3 0 0 1 4-10z">
                </path>
            </svg>
        </div>

        <div class="shape-loop">
            <svg width="40" height="40" viewBox="0 0 100 100" fill="none" stroke="#C4C6E5" stroke-width="12"
                stroke-linecap="round">
                <path d="M30,20 Q60,5 80,40 T50,90 T20,60" />
            </svg>
        </div>

        <div class="shape-scribbles">
            <svg width="80" height="100" viewBox="0 0 100 100" fill="none" stroke="#FFC07F" stroke-width="3">
                <path d="M80,10 Q90,20 85,30 T90,50" />
                <path d="M60,15 Q70,5 75,25 T80,40" />
                <path d="M90,5 Q100,15 95,25 T100,45" />
            </svg>
        </div>

        <div class="container">
            <div class="banner-content align-left">
                <span class="sub-heading">Agrim Classes</span>
                <h1 class="page-title">Specialized Crash Course</h1>
                <ul class="breadcrumb-list">
                    <li><a href="/">Home</a></li>
                    <li class="separator"><i class="fas fa-chevron-right"></i></li>
                    <li>Courses</li>
                    <li class="separator"><i class="fas fa-chevron-right"></i></li>
                    <li class="active">Crash Course</li>
                </ul>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>


    <section class="course-intro-creative">
        <div class="container">
            <div class="intro-grid">
                <div class="intro-main">
                    <span class="section-tag">Final Attempt to Success</span>
                    <h2 class="creative-heading">Transform Your Aspirations into <span class="highlight">Reality</span>
                    </h2>
                    <p class="creative-desc">
                        At Agrim Classes, we understand that the road to achieving your dream college can sometimes be
                        challenging, especially if previous attempts didn't yield the desired results. That's why our
                        specialized crash course is meticulously designed for students who may have struggled with prior
                        coaching or didn't perform as expected. We are here to provide unwavering support, focusing on
                        transforming your final attempt into a successful one.
                    </p>

                    <div class="highlight-box">
                        <h4><i class="fas fa-hand-holding-heart"></i> Personalized & Affordable</h4>
                        <p>
                            We emphasize building a solid foundation of core concepts to help you gain confidence. With
                            expert faculty members from prestigious institutions, you'll receive guidance from
                            individuals who deeply understand what it takes to succeed. Additionally, our affordable
                            fees ensure that top-quality education is accessible to all, without compromise.
                        </p>
                    </div>
                </div>

                <div class="intro-features">
                    <div class="feature-card-small">
                        <div class="icon-circle"><i class="fas fa-stopwatch"></i></div>
                        <h5>Exam Strategies & Tips</h5>
                        <p>We focus on equipping you with effective exam strategies, from time management techniques to
                            tips for dealing with exam pressure, all aimed at boosting your confidence.</p>
                    </div>
                    <div class="feature-card-small">
                        <div class="icon-circle"><i class="fas fa-tasks"></i></div>
                        <h5>Weekly Tests & Mocks</h5>
                        <p>To gauge your progress and sharpen your skills, we provide regular assessments, including
                            weekly tests and mock exams designed to replicate the actual exam experience.</p>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>

    <section class="boosters-section">
        <div class="" style="margin-left: 70px; margin-right: 70px; padding-top: 60px;">
            <div class="text-center mb-5">
                <h2 class="main-heading">Exam Preparation Boosters</h2>
            </div>

            <div class="boosters-grid">
                <div class="booster-card card-red">
                    <div class="icon-wrapper"><i class="fas fa-user-friends"></i></div>
                    <h4>India's Best<br>Ever Team</h4>
                </div>

                <div class="booster-card card-green">
                    <div class="icon-wrapper"><i class="fas fa-database"></i></div>
                    <h4>Small Batch Size<br>(Special 20)</h4>
                </div>

                <div class="booster-card card-dark-blue">
                    <div class="icon-wrapper"><i class="fas fa-book-open"></i></div>
                    <h4>Doubt Clearing<br>Session</h4>
                </div>

                <div class="booster-card card-light-blue">
                    <div class="icon-wrapper"><i class="far fa-building"></i></div>
                    <h4>Complete Study Package<br>(Online | Offline)</h4>
                </div>

                <div class="booster-card card-grey">
                    <div class="icon-wrapper"><i class="fas fa-download"></i></div>
                    <h4>Fortnight<br>Test</h4>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>

    <section class="eligibility-section">
        <div class="" style="margin-left: 70px; margin-right: 70px;">
            <h3 class="table-title">Crash Course Details</h3>

            <div class="table-wrapper">
                <table class="eligibility-table">
                    <thead>
                        <tr>
                            <th class="th-criteria">Eligibility criteria</th>
                            <th class="th-details">Details</th>
                        </tr>
                    </thead>
                    <tbody>
                        <tr>
                            <td class="criteria-name">Academic Qualifications</td>
                            <td>Students must be currently enrolled in Class 10, 11, 12, or Droppers preparing for
                                competitive exams like JEE, NEET, Olympiads, or Board Exams.</td>
                        </tr>
                        <tr>
                            <td class="criteria-name">Subjects Required</td>
                            <td>
                                Courses are available for:<br>
                                • JEE Crash Course – Physics, Chemistry, Mathematics<br>
                                • NEET Crash Course – Physics, Chemistry, Biology<br>
                                • Olympiad Crash Course – Mathematics, Science, English.
                            </td>
                        </tr>
                        <tr>
                            <td class="criteria-name">Age limit</td>
                            <td>No age restriction. Students should be preparing for their respective exams within the
                                eligible class range.</td>
                        </tr>
                        <tr>
                            <td class="criteria-name">Minimum Marks</td>
                            <td>No minimum marks required, but students should have basic subject knowledge as per their
                                syllabus.</td>
                        </tr>
                        <tr>
                            <td class="criteria-name">Mode of Teaching</td>
                            <td>Offline classes available. Recorded lectures, doubt-clearing sessions, and mentorship
                                may be provided.</td>
                        </tr>
                        <tr>
                            <td class="criteria-name">Course Duration</td>
                            <td>Varies from 4 weeks to 12 weeks, depending on the intensity of the course.</td>
                        </tr>
                        <tr>
                            <td class="criteria-name">Nationality</td>
                            <td>Indian and international students can enroll.</td>
                        </tr>
                        <tr>
                            <td class="criteria-name">Important Considerations</td>
                            <td>Live doubt-solving sessions are included in most crash courses. Study materials, test
                                series, and mock exams are provided.</td>
                        </tr>
                        <tr>
                            <td class="criteria-name">Exam Strategy & Tests</td>
                            <td>
                                • Regular mock tests, practice papers, and topic-wise quizzes.<br>
                                • Full-length test series and previous year paper discussions.<br>
                                • Personalized feedback and performance tracking.
                            </td>
                        </tr>
                    </tbody>
                </table>
            </div>

            <div class="course-cta text-center">
                <h3>Ready to fast-track your success?</h3>
                <a href="/contact" class="btn-primary">Join Crash Course Now <i class="fas fa-arrow-right"></i></a>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>

    <my-footer></my-footer>


<script src="footer.js"></script>
</body>